  "description": "<p>微软在开发Windows 8系统的时候特意为它带来了一项全新的功能--触屏。可谁也没想到的是，本来借助这项革新功能来吸引更多的用户，却没想到弄巧成拙，成了推广Win8的绊脚石。<strong>Creative Stategies总裁Tim Bajarin日前在《时代》发表文章指出，根据他所做的调查发现新引进的触屏功能成了微软公司决策的一大失误。</strong></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2eb46929/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244817.htm&amp;t=%E8%B0%83%E6%9F%A5%EF%BC%9A%E8%A7%A6%E5%B1%8F%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E6%88%90Windows+8%E6%8E%A8%E5%B9%BF%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%8A%E8%84%9A%E7%9F%B3\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244817.htm&amp;t=%E8%B0%83%E6%9F%A5%EF%BC%9A%E8%A7%A6%E5%B1%8F%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E6%88%90Windows+8%E6%8E%A8%E5%B9%BF%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%8A%E8%84%9A%E7%9F%B3\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244817.htm&amp;t=%E8%B0%83%E6%9F%A5%EF%BC%9A%E8%A7%A6%E5%B1%8F%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E6%88%90Windows+8%E6%8E%A8%E5%B9%BF%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%8A%E8%84%9A%E7%9F%B3\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244817.htm&amp;t=%E8%B0%83%E6%9F%A5%EF%BC%9A%E8%A7%A6%E5%B1%8F%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E6%88%90Windows+8%E6%8E%A8%E5%B9%BF%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%8A%E8%84%9A%E7%9F%B3\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244817.htm&amp;t=%E8%B0%83%E6%9F%A5%EF%BC%9A%E8%A7%A6%E5%B1%8F%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E6%8